snippet.title: goodbye.monster trailer
snippet.description:
Play at https://goodbye.monster/ ! 

goodbye.monster is a text-based browser game about agency and instrumentality in digital pet games. Players care for short-lived creatures, wander a post-apocalyptic text-based world, and learn to say goodbye as their creatures reach their inevitable ends.
